  "records": {
    "description": "Component which takes as input Full boxes of 9-1 compactable items, and crafts and merges them in the same operation at 8x HS. Only outputs full boxes of compacted items.",
    "features": [
      "11x14x6",
      "Can handle all 9-1 compactable recipes at 8x HS with one device",
      "Merges while Crafting, maximizing the efficiency of the loading operation"
    ],
    "considerations": [
      "No included whitelister",
      "Will Break if non full boxes are input",
      "Will break if non compactables are input"
    ],
    "notes": "Uses 8x compactor by XP_Bot, Civic, & geg, https://discordapp.com/channels/856232076252282890/1476718528513183969"
